          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">âš ï¸ Important Caveat: Etiology of Encephalitis Lethargica Remains Debated</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm mb-2">
            While the temporal coincidence is striking, <strong>modern studies have not confirmed</strong> 
